source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Conservation Elements - Ecological Integrity: Conservation Element Summary (HUC5)
source.description: This map presents summaries of conservation elements by reporting unit (HUC5) alongside terrestrial intactness and long-term potential for change.  This includes the NatureServe Species Summary dataset.
